896
01:50:30,239 --> 01:50:31,279
[SPEAKER_01] Kada je svijet propao.

897
01:50:31,520 --> 01:50:31,760
[SPEAKER_01] jer ima.

898
01:50:32,239 --> 01:50:33,199
