911
01:51:38,319 --> 01:51:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Hoćete čovjek pohvaliti, a ne nas?

912
01:51:40,640 --> 01:51:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Hoćete čovjek pohvaliti.

913
01:51:42,239 --> 01:51:47,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa momci, hvala vam puno inače na radu i na ovom sad tu dolazku.

914
